00:02:29.451 --> 00:02:30.607
of a human cornea,

00:02:30.631 --> 00:02:33.705
and on the right, we have
a radio telescope image

00:02:33.729 --> 00:02:36.349
of the star-forming region NGC-1333.

00:02:36.373 --> 00:02:39.106
Now, aside from the fact
that these images look similar

00:02:39.130 --> 00:02:42.053
