00:02:43.847 --> 00:02:46.590
the way the data comes
from the machine or the telescope

00:02:46.614 --> 00:02:48.216
is remarkably similar.

00:02:48.240 --> 00:02:50.720
Here's an MRI scanner.

00:02:50.744 --> 00:02:53.731
And if you've never seen
the raw data of a patient's brain,

00:02:53.755 --> 00:02:55.085
this is what it looks like.

00:02:55.109 --> 00:02:57.636
When the MRI scanner
is acquiring the data,

00:02:57.660 --> 00:02:58.945
